<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-09-26T10:15:26-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-09-26T10:15:26-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-26T10:15:26-04:00</updated><title>丰田普锐斯和 Rav4 不再是 Prime 车型</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;红色 Rav4 建筑物后四分之三视图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hTnPq8vbo3GNF-_aSH8TboE867A=/102x0:1946x1229/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73612382/2025_Toyota_RAV4_PHEV_XSE_Super sonic_Red_Hero_2048x1229.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;新款 2025 Rav4“插电式混合动力车”。&lt;/em>; |图片：丰田&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;tnCZqk&quot;>;丰田的普锐斯有其&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/11/16/23462123/2023-toyota- prius-glow-up-redesign-still-hybrid-not-ev&quot;>;2023 年的全面发光&lt;/a>;重新设计，现在汽车制造商也改变了它的名称。 2025 年 Prius Prime 现在将采用更简单的方式名称：普锐斯插电式混合动力车。 Rav4 Prime 也是如此，现在是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://pressroom.toyota.com/new-name-same-great-powertrain-for-the-2025-toyota-rav4-plug-in-混合动力/&quot;>;称为 Rav4 插电式混合动力车&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;7k0J6M&quot;>;丰田表示，更名“旨在帮助消费者更轻松地识别 Prius 和 Rav4 之间的动力总成选择”模型。 2025 年版的 Prius Plug-in 后部还将有更新的“PHEV”（插电式混合动力电动汽车）徽章。与此同时，Rav4 的前后丰田标志中将不再有蓝色光环。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;4BIv8K &quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;丰田普锐斯评论：电动汽车现实检查&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/23691342/toyota-prius-2023-review-hybrid-specs-photos-price&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;oxf9MF&quot; >;新款 2025 Prius 车型的规格似乎没有变化，否则 - 插电式版本仍然有...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/ 26/24254955/toyota-prius-rav4-plug-in-hybrid-drops-prime-2025&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254955/toyota-prius-rav4-plug-in-hybrid-drops-prime-2025" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254955/toyota-prius-rav4-plug-in-hybrid-drops-prime-2025</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-26T09:59:44-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-26T09:59:44-04:00</updated><title> LG 智能电视已开始在闲置时显示广告</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;LG 智能电视上显示的全屏汽车广告。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/L3UhPNg9A7DVccLS7OxzrKMBpkc=/60x0:1140x720/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73612301/LG_Screensaver_ad.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;这是新屏幕保护程序广告的示例。&lt;/em>; |图片：LG 广告解决方案&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;yRr2ZW&quot;>;LG 的智能电视在进入空闲模式时传统屏幕保护程序启动之前开始显示全屏广告。原生屏幕保护程序广告&lt;a href=&quot;https://lgads.tv/press_release/idle-time-is-not-wasted-time/&quot;>;本月早些时候开始在 LG 智能电视上推出&lt;/a>;，包括&lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/3/24023584/lg-2024-oled-tv-lineup-m4-g4-c4-b4-features-specs&quot;>;OLED，例如新款 G4型号&lt;/a>;，并将出现在主屏幕、内容商店和 LG 频道上。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;8XT2w7&quot;>;该功能将通过 &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.flatpanelshd.com/news.php?subaction=showfull&amp;amp;id=1727255253&quot;>;&lt;em>;FlatpanelsHD&lt;/em>; 报道&lt;/a>; 它看到了 LG Channels 流媒体服务以及来自第三方的静音广告这可能与电视或娱乐完全无关。 LG 广告解决方案技术主管戴夫·鲁德尼克 (Dave Rudnick) 在一份新闻稿中表示，这些广告在测试中非常有效，并且“为品牌提供了在最大屏幕上占据前沿和中心位置的宝贵机会......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254935/lg-smart-tv-oled-screensaver-ads-idle-mode&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p >; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254935/lg-smart-tv-oled-screensaver-ads-idle-mode" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254935/lg-smart-tv-oled-screensaver-ads-idle-mode</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-26T09:53:09-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-26T09:53:09-04:00</updated><title>加州新法律迫使数字商店承认您只是授权内容，而不是购买内容</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;两只手从手机中伸出的插图，一只手拿着信用卡，另一只手拿着现金。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ro1tpnWB08rFXNziyDcsJT0l6c0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73612286/STK417_Mobile_Banking_1.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Hugo Herrera / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;fAYnBI&quot;>;加州州长 Gavin Newsom 签署了一项法律 (&lt;a href=&quot;https://digitaldemocracy.calmatters.org/ bills/ca_202320240ab2426&quot;>;AB 2426&lt;/a>;），以打击数字游戏、电影、音乐和电子书的“消失”购买。该立法将迫使数字店面告诉客户他们只是获得了使用数字媒体的许可证，而不是暗示他们实际上拥有该数字媒体。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;FWkQPr&quot;>;该法律明年生效时，它将禁止数字店面使用“购买”或“购买”等术语，除非他们告知顾客他们无法不受限制地访问他们所购买的任何东西。店面必须告诉顾客他们正在获得可以撤销的许可证，并提供随之而来的所有限制的列表。违反规定的公司可能会因虚假信息而被罚款...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254922/california-digital-purchase-disclosure -law-ab-2426&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254922/california-digital-purchase-disclosure-law-ab-2426" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254922/california-digital-purchase-disclosure-law-ab-2426</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-26T09:45:01-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-26T09:45:01-04:00</updated><title>在哪里预订 PS5 Pro 和 PlayStation 30 周年纪念系列</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;PlayStation 5 Pro 和控制器。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/QSFMytm84sXqPDb6bA5jDj4xIkk=/0x0:2700x1800/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73612266/ps5_pro_sean_hollister_verge_003.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;标准 PS5 Pro 看起来可能不如 30 周年纪念版那么酷，但它可能会更容易上手。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Sean Hollister / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;DAS7D8&quot;>;随着 PS5 Pro 交错预购计划的开始，我们距离 PlayStation 5 的中期更新越来越近了。这款售价 699.99 美元的游戏机将于&lt;strong>;美国东部时间上午 10 点/太平洋时间上午 7 点&lt;/strong>;通过索尼的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp; ;url=https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-consoles%2Fplaystation5-pro-console&amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F24252575 %2Fsony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;PlayStation Direct 店面&lt;/a>;，所以如果您想尽快获得一个，您会想要在索尼的网站上排队（请务必准备好您的 PlayStation Network 登录信息）。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;rRD9pe&quot;>;同时进行预购的还有 &lt;a href =&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/19/24249013/sony-playstation-ps5-pro-30th-anniversary-retro&quot;>;索尼复古风格 30 周年纪念&lt;/a>; PS5 Pro 捆绑包（&lt; a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-consoles%2Fplaystation5-pro-console- 30 周年限量版捆绑包%3Femcid%3Dot-ps-456950&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F24252575%2Fsony-ps5-pro-playstation-5- preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;$999.99&lt;/a>;)，PS5 数字版 slim (&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com? id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-consoles%2Fplaystation5-digital-edition-30th-anniversary-limited-edition-bundle-model-group- slim%3Femcid%3Dot-ps-456950&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F24252575%2Fsony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release-日期&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;$499.99&lt;/a>;)，PlayStation Portal (&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url= https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-accessories%2Fplaystation-portal-remote-player-30th-anniversary-limited-edition%3Femcid%3Dot-ps-456950&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp; sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F24252575%2Fsony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;219.99 美元&lt;/a>;), DualSense (&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy -accessories%2Fdualsense-wireless-controller-30th-anniversary-limited-edition%3Femcid%3Dot-ps-456950&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F24252575%2Fsony-ps5 -pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;79.99 美元&lt;/a>;) 和 DualSense Edge (&lt;a href=&quot;https:// go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-accessories%2Fdualsense-edge-wireless-controller-30th-anniversary-limited- Edition%3Femcid%3Dot-ps-456950&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F24252575%2Fsony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release- date&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;$219.99&lt;/a>;)。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;VXBtUl&quot;>;但是，如果您在队列中运气不好，请预订标准版 PS5 Pro 在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/cm93fQtADXd&quot;>;Best Buy&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706 等零售商处购买/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FPLAYSTATION-PS5-PRO-CONSOLE%2F11839818124&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;W. ..&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24252575/sony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24252575/sony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24252575/sony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release-date</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-26T09:04:58-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-26T09:04:58-04:00</updated><title>谷歌表示，封闭的广告生态系统并不反竞争，只是更安全</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;充满不同产品广告的页面的照片拼贴。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/EYoCD2dVVOPswMEqU4z1H-9akkw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73612180/STK445_ADVERTISING_STK093_GOOGLE_A.0 .jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge、Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;v6Q71c&quot;>;谷歌本周在法庭上借鉴了一本熟悉的剧本，为自己辩护通过提出安全问题来实施反竞争行为。虽然政府声称其锁定广告技术市场是为了赚更多钱，但谷歌的证人表示，更封闭的生态系统对于用户来说往往更安全——这与谷歌和苹果对其移动应用商店的辩护相呼应。&lt;/p>; &lt; p id=&quot;mthekO&quot;>;谷歌的律师在过去几天里一直在针对司法部进行辩护。该公司辩称，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/24/24253293/google-ad-tech-antitrust-trial-doj-case&quot;>;司法部将其行为视为反竞争行为&lt;/a>; — 例如&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/11/24241386/former-news-corp-executive-google-doj-ad-tech-Trial&quot;>;锁定客户其服务&lt;/a>;并发挥&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240386/google-doj-ad-tech-antitrust-trial-court-day-one&quot; >;通过其主导地位控制行业规则&lt;/a>;——实际上有正当的商业目的。要点...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24253523/google-close-ad-ecosystem-awbid-ad-fraud-3ve &quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24253523/google-closed-ad-ecosystem-awbid-ad-fraud-3ve" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24253523/google-close-ad-ecosystem-awbid-ad-fraud-3ve</id><author><name>劳伦·费纳</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-26T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-26T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title>徕卡推出第二款Q3相机，配备新镜头，价格更高</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Leica Q3 43 和 Leica Q3 的俯视图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/I30189kvSetY3unmMLHgJk6eucA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73612110/19084_Leica_Q3_43_Ambient_09_HiRe s_crop.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;现在有两个了！&lt;/em>; |图片：徕卡相机&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;YeKv2R&quot;>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;SSRlmK&quot;>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;QC5bvW&quot;>;徕卡Q系列全系列自 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2015/6/10/8754047/leica-q-camera-announcement-price-hands-on- launch&quot;>;最初是在 2015 年&lt;/a>;，但现在该公司正在进行重组。今天推出的徕卡 Q3 43 与 60 兆像素几乎相同 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/25/23736639/leica-q3-camera-28mm-fixed-lens-compact -8k-availability-price-specs&quot;>;Q3&lt;/a>;，但它配备了 43mm f/2 镜头，视野更窄，更适合特写和肖像——当然，它更贵，价格为 6,895 美元，而标准型号为 6,295 美元。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;UGpTcZ&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot; readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Fujifilm X100VI vs. Ricoh GR IIIx：最佳傻瓜相机之战&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/24118170/fujifilm-x100vi-ricoh-gr-iiix-point-shoot-camera-comparison&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;制造相机的打印机公司再打印一个版本&quot;, &quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24158218/ricoh-gr-iii-hdf-full-frame-video&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;MH3qyA&quot;>;Q3 43 的规格基本相同，因为它基本上是一款 Q3 相机，永久安装了新的非球面 APO-Summicron 43mm f/2 镜头和灰色人造革（我想财力雄厚的用户不可避免地会同时购买这两款相机）可以区分它们在袋子里）。它使用相同的背照式传感器...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254024/leica-q3-43-full -frame-fixed-lens-43mm-camera-price-specs&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254024/leica-q3-43-full-frame-fixed-lens-43mm-camera-price-specs" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254024/leica-q3-43-full-frame-fixed-lens-43mm-camera-price-specs</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-26T08:40:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-26T08:40:00-04:00</updated><title>克里斯汀·贝尔 (Kristen Bell) 在成为 Instagram 官方代言人之前告诉 Instagram“摆脱人工智能”</title><content type="html"> &lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;“没人想要这个”- 照片通话&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/tCWsGEjXJRqdlAkOqUr3qTBabdY=/191x0:5816x3750/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/73612081/2172054681.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Tommaso Boddi / Variety via Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;eTKg2k&quot;>;Meta 已经削减了高-演员资料&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/e/24017461&quot;>;将他们的声音&lt;/a>;发送给 Meta AI 聊天机器人，克里斯汀·贝尔 (Kristen Bell) 就是首批声音之一。贝尔的声音让人有点惊讶。早在 6 月份，她就公开表示反对 Meta 的人工智能使用她的数据。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;tg9x9k&quot;>;她转发了一条 Instagram 热门消息，宣称她拒绝同意 Meta 使用她的内容和肖像来训练大语言模特并要求 Instagram“摆脱人工智能程序”。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;Kristen Bell / Instagram&lt;/cite>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;hMzBBr&quot; >;该提示声称，通过重新发布，用户拒绝 Meta 将其个人数据用于这些目的的许可。杰西卡·查斯坦、莎拉·保罗森和阿什丽·提斯代尔等名人 &lt;a href=&quot;https://thetab.com/uk/2024/09/25/what-is-goodbye-meta-ai-post-instagram-hoax-388529 &quot;>;已重新发布此提示的最新版本&lt;/a>; —...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24253834/kristen- Bell-meta-ai-voice-connect&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24253834/kristen-bell-meta-ai-voice-connect" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24253834/kristen-bell-meta-ai-voice-connect</id><author><name>凯莉罗宾逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-26T07:13:15-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-26T07:13:15-04:00</updated><title>谷歌地图正在打击虚假评论</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Google 地图徽标的矢量插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/TiO_23vYCDuKiMmkSnmfH8WfUSs=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73611927/STK270_GOOGLE_MAPS_D.0.png&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;如果某个地点被发现使用虚假评论，Google 将暂时完全限制其评论。&lt;/em>; |图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;jRU1sR&quot;>;Google 地图在商业页面中出现虚假评论，并向用户突出显示此类活动。 Google 现在将对违反搜索巨头虚假参与政策的&lt;a href=&quot;https://support.google.com/business/answer/14114287&quot;>;商家资料施加限制&lt;/a>;，例如暂时删除评论、屏蔽新评论或评级，并在已删除虚假评论的个人资料上显示警告消息。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;u8iG0A&quot;>;英国今年早些时候引入了企业个人资料限制，但 &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.seroundtable.com/google-reviews-restrictions-business-profile-violations-38068.html&quot;>;&lt;em>;搜索引擎圆桌会议&lt;/em>;指出&lt;/a>;支持页面已于中期更新- 九月似乎在全球范围内适用。不过，目前只有英国用户会看到业务警告，例如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/mblumenthal/status/1835746813032177806&quot;>;Mike Blumenthal 发布到 X 的示例&lt;/a >;.&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：Google / &lt;a class=&quot;ql-link&quot; href=&quot;https://x.com/mblumenthal/status/1835746813032177806&quot; 目标=&quot;_blank&quot;>;迈克...&lt;/a>;&lt;/cite>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254882/google-maps -removing-fake-business-reviews-warning-message&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254882/google-maps-removing-fake-business-reviews-warning-message" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254882/google-maps-removing-fake-business-reviews-warning-message</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-26T00:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-26T00:00:00-04:00</updated><title> SteelSeries 推出售价 160 美元的 Xbox、PlayStation 或 PC 游戏耳机</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;SteelSeries Arctis GameBuds&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Opz5jOOLg5wwMKqvXWZatKGu4eo=/14x0:1987x1315/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image /image/73611574/pr_arctis_gamebuds_white_lifestyle_woman_indoor_02.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：SteelSeries&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;3Bd8XH&quot;>;SteelSeries 打造了新款耳塞，旨在与 Xbox、PlayStation、 Nintendo Switch 游戏机，甚至 PC 和手机。售价 159.99 美元的 Arctis GameBuds 包括主动降噪 (ANC)、Qi 无线充电以及在移动蓝牙使用和游戏机或 PC 游戏之间即时切换的功能。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;cGtApP&quot;>;过去几天我一直在尝试它们，到目前为止，我印象深刻，但我需要更多时间进行全面审查。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;tl7d8T&quot;>;Arctis GameBuds 看起来与市场上大多数耳塞非常相似，配有各种硅胶耳塞，适合不同的耳朵形状。 SteelSeries 使用四麦克风 ANC 系统来阻挡您游戏时的声音，如果您想听到环境声音，还有透明模式...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24253924/steelseries-arctis-gamebuds-earbuds-pc-xbox-playstation-nintendo-switch-release-date-pricing&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24253924/steelseries-arctis-gamebuds-earbuds-pc-xbox-playstation-nintendo-switch-release-date-pricing" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24253924/steelseries-arctis-gamebuds-earbuds-pc-xbox-playstation-nintendo-switch-release-date-pricing</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-25T19:21:34-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-25T19:21:34-04:00</updated><title>现在最值得购买的任天堂 Switch 控制器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;各种 Nintendo Switch 控制器的照片拼贴。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/UnfFceeTyhhAetFGkI7eiKNkmfc=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/71435209/247143_Buying_Guide_Switch_Controllers_CVirginia.6 .jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;从无与伦比的 Switch Pro 和舒适的 Joy-Con 替代品，到让您在 Switch 上使用 Xbox 或 PlayStation 控制器的加密狗，这些是您可以获得的最好的 Switch 控制器。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23350899/nintendo-switch-controllers-best-wireless-joy-con-gamepad&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/ p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23350899/nintendo-switch-controllers-best-wireless-joy-con-gamepad" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23350899/nintendo-switch-controllers-best-wireless-joy-con-gamepad</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name><name>卡梅伦·福克纳</name></author></entry></feed>